### How to Create the CSV Files
1. Copy each CSV block below into a text editor.
2. Save as `amino_acids_atoms.csv` and `amino_acids_bonds.csv` in the same directory as your program.
3. Run the program with: `./amino_visualizer amino_acids_atoms.csv amino_acids_bonds.csv`
